---
const siteTitle = "Busshouji";

import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---

<html lang="ja">
	<head>
		<meta charset="utf-8" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
		<link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
		<meta name="generator" content={Astro.generator} />
		<title>{siteTitle}</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />

		<main>
			<section class="hero" aria-label="メインビジュアル">
				<img src="/images/hero/home-hero.webp" alt="ヒーロー画像" loading="eager" />
				<div class="hero-overlay">
					<p class="hero-subtitle">BUSSHOUJI WEBSITE</p>
					<h1>仏生寺の魅力を、静かに、丁寧に。</h1>
					<p>
						歴史、風景、行事の情報を通して、
						訪れる人と地域をつなぐためのホームページです。
					</p>
				</div>
			</section>

			<div class="content-wrap">
				<section id="overview" class="info-section">
					<figure class="media media-overview">
						<img src="/images/other/image.webp" alt="仏生寺の概要イメージ" loading="lazy" />
					</figure>
					<div class="info-text">
						<p class="section-label">Overview</p>
						<h2>概要</h2>
						<p>
							仏生寺は、地域とともに歩み続ける寺院です。静かな境内と四季折々の表情、
							そして地域の行事を通して、人と人が自然につながる場所を目指しています。
						</p>
					</div>
				</section>

				<section id="news" class="info-section">
					<div class="info-text">
						<p class="section-label">News</p>
						<h2>お知らせ</h2>
						<ul class="news-list">
							<li>
								<time datetime="2026-01-01">2026/01/01</time>
								<p>【年末年始のご案内】初詣について</p>
							</li>
							<li>
								<time datetime="2026-04-23">2026/04/23</time>
								<p>それぞれの季節ごとのお知らせについて</p>
							</li>
							<li>
								<time datetime="2026-04-23">2026/04/23</time>
								<p>
									それぞれの季節ごとのお知らせについて<br />
									一応改行されることも想定しています
								</p>
							</li>
						</ul>
						<a class="news-link" href="/news">お知らせ一覧へ</a>
					</div>
					<figure class="media media-news">
						<img src="/images/other/image-2.webp" alt="お知らせイメージ" loading="lazy" />
					</figure>
				</section>
			</div>
		</main>

		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>

<style>
	:root {
		color: #1f2b24;
		background-color: #f2f0eb;
		font-family: "Hiragino Mincho ProN", "Yu Mincho", "Times New Roman", serif;
	}

	* {
		box-sizing: border-box;
	}

	body {
		margin: 0;
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, #f8f4ed 0%, #f2f0eb 40%, #ebe7df 100%);
	}

	main {
		padding-top: 80px;
	}

	.hero {
		position: relative;
		width: 100%;
		height: 640px;
		overflow: hidden;
	}

	.hero img {
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		object-fit: cover;
		object-position: center center;
		display: block;
	}

	.hero-overlay {
		position: absolute;
		inset: 0;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		justify-content: flex-end;
		padding: 0 80px 76px;
		background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12) 0%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.4) 65%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.58) 100%);
		color: #fff;
	}

	.hero-subtitle {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.2em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		opacity: 0.9;
	}

	h1 {
		margin: 0.8rem 0 1rem;
		font-size: clamp(2rem, 3.3vw, 3rem);
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
		line-height: 1.3;
	}

	.hero-overlay p {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 1rem;
		line-height: 1.9;
	}

	.content-wrap {
		width: min(1120px, calc(100% - 80px));
		margin: 100px auto 100px;
		display: grid;
		gap: 200px;
	}

	.info-section {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
		align-items: start;
		gap: 40px;
		padding: 0;
	}

	.section-label {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 0.78rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.16em;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		color: #7e6d52;
	}

	h2 {
		margin: 0.65rem 0 1rem;
		font-size: 2rem;
		letter-spacing: 0.05em;
		color: #2f2518;
	}

	.info-text {
		margin: auto 0;
	}

	.info-text p {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 1rem;
		line-height: 2;
		color: #3d3225;
	}

	.news-list {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
	}

	.news-list li {
		padding: 25px 0;
		border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(84, 70, 50, 0.3);
	}

	.news-list time {
		display: block;
		font-size: 15px;
		letter-spacing: 0.08em;
		color: #112e1e;
		/* margin-bottom: 5px; */
	}

	.news-list p {
		margin: 0;
		font-size: 1.3rem;
		line-height: 1.9;
		color: #2f2518;
	}

	.news-link {
		display: flex;
		justify-content: end;
		align-items: center;
		align-self: flex-start;
		gap: 0.4rem;
		margin-top: 50px;
		font-size: 0.95rem;
		text-decoration: none;
		color: #2f2518;
		letter-spacing: 0.08em;
	}

	.news-link::before {
		content: "=>";
		font-size: 0.95rem;
	}

	.media {
		margin: 0;
		border-radius: 16px;
		overflow: hidden;
		/* aspect-ratio: 1280 / 853; */
		aspect-ratio: 800 /900;
	}

	.media img {
		width: 100%;
		height: 100%;
		object-fit: cover;
		display: block;
	}

	.media-overview img {
		object-position: center center;
	}

	.media-news img {
		object-position: center bottom;
	}

	.media-news {
		/* aspect-ratio: 800 /900; */
	}

</style>
